#way to install gatk4 with all the useful tools to call variants but also to manipulate vcf files.
The code:

Conda install -c bioconda gatk4,vcftools,samtools,bedtools,bcftools,bwa,picard,fastqc,igv,nextflow

Nextflow is useful if you wanna use sarek pipeline.

You can put all the above tools in a separate conda environment via conda create --name myenv then conda install the above tools.

